catch
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a last sheep in a catching pen to be shorn before a run is completed or any sheep taken from a catching-pen to be shorn.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
